  "body": "<p>Excited to have contributed 2 projects to <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/preorder/jubilee-e-book-and-kit?aff=6cc2c70f\">Studio Calico's Jubilee e-book</a>!</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/b733066efbd75add.jpg?v=1782526355\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Studio Calico has put together an amazing collection of inspiration – 100 projects in all – and paired it with an amazing kit filled with exclusive product. Download a free sample of the Jubilee e-book <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/digital/free/jubilee-sample?aff=6cc2c70f\">here</a>.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"7b-jubileecontributors-600x260.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/8495ea8e11249bdd.jpg?v=1782526358\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"7c-FREE-SHIPPING-KIT-IMAGE-600x471.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/7ad9c23ed359d639.jpg?v=1782526361\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>The stamp set is one of my favorites ever (yes, for real) - I have been using it a ton for personal and client projects. Here's a little sneak at one of the spreads I created for the <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/preorder/jubilee-e-book-and-kit?aff=6cc2c70f\">ebook</a>:</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/ab8eb9c878a3b026.jpg?v=1782526364\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Head to the <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/preorder/jubilee-e-book-and-kit?aff=6cc2c70f\">presale page</a> for full details on what’s included, and to take advantage of the special presale offer (it’s valid through November 17th).</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
}